{
  "text": "First passage and seeded cells were plated and methanol-fixed as described. [CITATION_1] 15 Slides were blocked with 1% BSA in PBS, incubated with primary antibodies against CD31 (1:1000, Santa Cruz), vWF (1:500, DAKO), and ␣-SMA Clone 1A4 (1:2000, Sigma) followed by fluorescein-conjugated secondary antibodies (Vector Laboratories). Slides were examined and photographed under a fluorescence microscope (Nikon Eclipse TE2000).",
